message.body: Hey -- my roommate is away this weekend with her boyfriend and I don't have to go to NJ for anything so I have nothing to do this weekend. If you end up being free at all, let me know. Hope your photographing went well
This sound great. I will find something productive for us to do haha
Hell yeah! I'm helping my brother write his college essay (aka writing it for him) so I am in no mood to be productive lol
If you are free tonight, I am stopping by my friends bartending shift around 9 to have a hot toddy with him. I know that isn't very productive but it will be fun. I can pick you up obviously.
